Package: MiniMaxApprox
Type: Package
Title: Implemention of Remez Algorithm for Polynomial and Rational Function
    Approximation
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(given="Avraham", family="Adler",role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    email="Avraham.Adler@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3039-0703"))
Description: Implements the basic Remez algorithm for polynomial approximation
